data.title: TEDxCIC
data.meta_description: TED.com, home of TED Talks, is a global initiative about ideas worth spreading via TEDx, The Audacious Project, TED Books, TED Conferences, TED-Ed and more.
data.text:
Ahmed Badawy

A computer programmer who give lectures in Science In Five Academy, and also a human development specialist. He combined between Studying and training presentation, communication and psychology personalities skills.

Germeen El-Manadily

Regional Director for Roznameh Group for publishing and Translation. She managed to reach a leading position in one of the most difficult field where her age didn't exceed 28. She began her career at the age of 18 from the point she joined university, and in 2015 she joined a publishing career. Published more than 40 edition over two years. Under her administration, Roznameh had published several translated Egyptian books by Yusuf Idris, Salah Jahin, Abdul Rahman Al-Janoudi and Ibrahim Abdul Majid. In 2016 she organized an initiative to discover young talents in writing, resulting 150 new jobs.

Hesham Mansour

Hesham Mansour is an Egyptian writer, actor and content creator who adds a contemporary view on life in his creations with a little sprinkling of humor. His early career life sparkled on social media for its comedy sketches adaptations. Adding a new sarcasm for everyday life activities.

Islam Anan

An enthusiast entrepreneur and creator of the jargon "employee-entrepreneurship"

Menna Aldawy

Menna Aldawy is an exceptional person who always can leave a mark wherever she goes. with a smile! She developed a remarkable mindset that highlights self-value and personality as both two perks that upon her experiences, delivers human's uniqueness to the next level.

Menna Eldawi

Menna Eldawi is an exceptional person who always can leave a mark wherever she goes. with a smile! She developed a remarkable mindset that highlights self-value and personality as both two perks that upon her experiences, delivers human's uniqueness to the next level.

Mostafa Badr

First Egyptian male Ironman race finisher who took the hard decision after 2 years working with a previous minister as business administrator to shift his career to become an airline captain. He traveled to the Canadian Ottawa university to do what he wants what he loves. He believes that your imagination and your dreams should be the center of your life. He is a kitesurfer and an advanced Padi diver, Working on his masters now in Frankfurt university of applied sciences.

Nora Mohammed

An artist and designer, she graduated from the school of engineering but she decided to study Digital Art, her journey started by selling in international and American websites where she designed 800 unique designs and sold more than 900 product most of them in America, Australia, Canada and Europe.

Omar Abdulsalam

Omar is an enthusiast young inventor, His main interest focuses on inventing new solutions for people. While it some events took him on focusing at the PWD needs as a priority. will his inventions help innovate millions of people's lives ?

Rehab Hany

Rehab Hany is a Broadcaster at radio NRJ, and an editor in chief at the CBC channels ,was a voice actor in Disney’s “brave” and she also wrote 3 books (klam fady , elghata we elhala and abour el-hawadyt)

Tawfik Almenshawy

Tawfik is an original stand-up comedy, He has been in the career for over 5 years, In this time he had already been a top comedian. known for his approach to cover daily questions and Egyptian modern satire. While making a full of fun stand-up comedy session , he might add at the ending a different serious flavor to leave people with a unique experience and considerations for different points of view in life.

Tawfik Elmenshawy

A stand up comedian who started his career in 2013. He hosted many concerts in "El-Sawy Culture Wheel" and many other places. He was chosen to star "Stand up Arabian" movie. He also was chosen to present Egypt in comedian central in Dubai.
